The hotel is gorgeous and our room was clean, modern, and just as I expected a Luxury Starwood Hotel should be.	The rooms are pretty standard for a luxury hotel; I'm SPG platinum and find I get a suite upgrade more often at the W but rarely at the Joule.	I have stayed in the finest resorts in the world and Starwood has placed this hotel in their Luxury Collection.	This was part of the Starwood Luxury Collection, but having been dissappointed many times before, I did not expect much.	We booked this hotel under luxury hotel and resort collection.